Package: meToolkit
Type: Package
Title: Build and Customize Phewas Multimorbidity Explorer Apps. 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nick Strayer
Maintainer: Nick Strayer <nick.strayer@gmail.com>
Description: The main function in this package spins up a fully contained and self-hosted copy of an ME app for data privacy. 
    In addition to, multiple functions are provided allowing the user to customize their app from pre-loading data to configuring 
    the individual charts included. 
